  "hashtags": ["#PCBDesign", "#PCBChecklist", "#DesignForManufacturing", "#DFM", "#ElectronicsDesign", "#CuCircuits", "#HardwareEngineering", "#MakeInIndia"],
  "caption": "Stop. Before you send that Gerber file, run through this checklist.\n\nWe see it every week at Cu Circuits: boards that come back with avoidable errors. Wrong trace widths. Missing decoupling caps. Silkscreen over pads. Drill holes too close to the edge.\n\nThese are not complex problems. They are checklist problems.\n\nHere are 10 critical checks every hardware engineer should run before hitting 'Order PCB.' Save this post. Print it. Tape it to your monitor.\n\nBecause a $5 checklist review today saves a $500 respin next week.\n\nWhich check do you most often forget? Drop it in the comments.\n\n#PCBDesign #PCBChecklist #DesignForManufacturing #DFM #ElectronicsDesign #CuCircuits #HardwareEngineering #MakeInIndia",
  "strategy": {"format": "checklist_scorecard", "visual_approach": "green checkmarks and red X marks with importance indicators"},
  "html": "<div style=\"width:1080px; height:1350px; background:#0D0D0D; position:relative; overflow:hidden; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;\">\n\n  <!-- Subtle grid background -->\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:100%; background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(184,115,51,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(184,115,51,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 40px 40px;\"></div>\n\n  <!-- Cu Logo -->\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:36px; left:40px; width:64px; height:64px; background:#B87333; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:28px; font-weight:800; color:#0D0D0D; letter-spacing:1px;\">Cu</div>\n\n  <!-- Top accent line -->\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:4px; background:linear-gradient(90deg, #B87333, #2E8B57, #B87333);\"></div>\n\n  <!-- Header -->\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:36px; left:130px; right:40px;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:14px; color:#B87333; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:3px; text-transform:uppercase;\">BEFORE YOU FAB</div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:100px; left:40px; right:40px;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:48px; font-weight:800; color:#FFFFFF; line-height:1.15; letter-spacing:-1px;\">PCB Design Review<br>Checklist</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-top:12px;\">10 checks that save you from costly respins</div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Checklist Items -->\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:270px; left:40px; right:40px;\">\n\n    <!-- Item 1 -->\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; padding:16px 20px; margin-bottom:8px; background:rgba(46,139,87,0.1); border-left:4px solid #2E8B57; border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:28px; margin-right:16px;\">&#9989;</div>\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:18px; font-weight:700; color:#FFFFFF;\">Run DRC (Design Rule Check)</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:13px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-top:2px;\">Zero errors, zero warnings before export</div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"margin-left:auto; background:#FF4444; color:white; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; padding:3px 10px; border-radius:12px;\">CRITICAL</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Item 2 -->\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; padding:16px 20px; margin-bottom:8px; background:rgba(46,139,87,0.1); border-left:4px solid #2E8B57; border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:28px; margin-right:16px;\">&#9989;</div>\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:18px; font-weight:700; color:#FFFFFF;\">Verify Trace Widths for Current</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:13px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-top:2px;\">Use a trace width calculator for power lines</div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"margin-left:auto; background:#FF4444; color:white; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; padding:3px 10px; border-radius:12px;\">CRITICAL</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Item 3 -->\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; padding:16px 20px; margin-bottom:8px; background:rgba(46,139,87,0.1); border-left:4px solid #2E8B57; border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:28px; margin-right:16px;\">&#9989;</div>\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:18px; font-weight:700; color:#FFFFFF;\">Decoupling Caps on Every IC</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:13px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-top:2px;\">100nF close to power pins, short traces</div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"margin-left:auto; background:#FF4444; color:white; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; padding:3px 10px; border-radius:12px;\">CRITICAL</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Item 4 -->\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; padding:16px 20px; margin-bottom:8px; background:rgba(184,115,51,0.1); border-left:4px solid #B87333; border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:28px; margin-right:16px;\">&#9989;</div>\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:18px; font-weight:700; color:#FFFFFF;\">LVS (Layout vs Schematic) Check</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:13px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-top:2px;\">Board must match schematic exactly</div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"margin-left:auto; background:#FF8800; color:white; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; padding:3px 10px; border-radius:12px;\">HIGH</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Item 5 -->\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; padding:16px 20px; margin-bottom:8px; background:rgba(184,115,51,0.1); border-left:4px solid #B87333; border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:28px; margin-right:16px;\">&#9989;</div>\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:18px; font-weight:700; color:#FFFFFF;\">Check Board Outline &amp; Mounting Holes</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:13px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-top:2px;\">Mechanical fit with enclosure confirmed</div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"margin-left:auto; background:#FF8800; color:white; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; padding:3px 10px; border-radius:12px;\">HIGH</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Item 6 -->\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; padding:16px 20px; margin-bottom:8px; background:rgba(184,115,51,0.1); border-left:4px solid #B87333; border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:28px; margin-right:16px;\">&#9989;</div>\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:18px; font-weight:700; color:#FFFFFF;\">Silkscreen Not Over Pads</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:13px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-top:2px;\">Clear silkscreen from solderable areas</div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"margin-left:auto; background:#FF8800; color:white; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; padding:3px 10px; border-radius:12px;\">HIGH</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Item 7 -->\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; padding:16px 20px; margin-bottom:8px; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border-left:4px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3); border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:28px; margin-right:16px;\">&#9989;</div>\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:18px; font-weight:700; color:#FFFFFF;\">Verify Drill Sizes &amp; Annular Rings</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:13px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-top:2px;\">Min annular ring per your fab's capability</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Item 8 -->\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; padding:16px 20px; margin-bottom:8px; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border-left:4px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3); border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:28px; margin-right:16px;\">&#9989;</div>\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:18px; font-weight:700; color:#FFFFFF;\">Copper Pour / Ground Plane Connected</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:13px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-top:2px;\">No floating copper islands</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Item 9 -->\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; padding:16px 20px; margin-bottom:8px; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border-left:4px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3); border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:28px; margin-right:16px;\">&#9989;</div>\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:18px; font-weight:700; color:#FFFFFF;\">Test Points for Debug Access</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:13px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-top:2px;\">Probe points on key signals and power rails</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Item 10 -->\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; padding:16px 20px; margin-bottom:8px; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border-left:4px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3); border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:28px; margin-right:16px;\">&#9989;</div>\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:18px; font-weight:700; color:#FFFFFF;\">Generate &amp; Inspect Gerber Files</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:13px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-top:2px;\">Open in a viewer before sending to fab</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Bottom stat bar -->\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; bottom:80px; left:40px; right:40px; display:flex; gap:20px;\">\n    <div style=\"flex:1; background:rgba(255,68,68,0.15); border-radius:12px; padding:16px; text-align:center;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:13px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);\">Avg Respin Cost</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:28px; font-weight:800; color:#FF4444;\">$2,500+</div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"flex:1; background:rgba(255,136,0,0.15); border-radius:12px; padding:16px; text-align:center;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:13px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);\">Time Lost</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:28px; font-weight:800; color:#FF8800;\">2+ Weeks</div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"flex:1; background:rgba(46,139,87,0.15); border-radius:12px; padding:16px; text-align:center;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:13px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);\">Errors Caught</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:28px; font-weight:800; color:#2E8B57;\">80%+</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Footer -->\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; bottom:24px; left:40px; right:40px; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:14px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3); font-weight:600;\">cucircuits.com</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:12px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);\">Save this. Run it every time.</div>\n  </div>\n\n</div>"
}
